How to install CNVScan

Common Process

   1. Download the compressed library.

   2. Uncompress the file into a directory which you want.

      $ tar xvfz CNVScan-1.2.1.tgz

   3. Download and install gbfp (http://code.google.com/p/gbfp/)


Install gbfp (required)

   1. gbfp a GenBank flatfile parser library with high speed can be found at
	http://code.google.com/p/gbfp/

   2. Follow the installation instructions before install CNVScan

Install CNVScan

   1. Make and install the library

      $ cd CNVScan-1.2.1
      $ make


   2. Launch CNVScan

      $ ./CNVScan <options>

